==Spanish==

===Phrase===
'''[[te#Spanish|te]] [[quiero]]'''

# [[I love you]]; I care about you.
#: Shows affection, love, or care, but not lust. ''Te quiero'' is often said to family members or friends. By contrast, ''[[te amo]]'' ("I love you") is usually reserved for one's lover.

